@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = Bearer <seu-jwt-aqui>

### Criar solicitação de agendamento
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking-requests/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "client_id": "<uuid-do-cliente>",
  "professional_id": "<uuid-do-profissional>",
  "address_id": "<uuid-do-endereco>",
  "proposed_value": 150.00,
  "schedule_details": {
    "recurrence": [
      { "day_of_week": "MONDAY", "start_time": "13:00", "end_time": "17:00" },
      { "day_of_week": "WEDNESDAY", "start_time": "13:00", "end_time": "17:00" }
    ],
    "start_date": "2026-06-10",
    "end_date": "2026-07-10"
  }
}

### Buscar por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking-requests/<id>
Authorization: {{token}}

### Listar por cliente
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking-requests/client/<client-id>
Authorization: {{token}}

### Listar por profissional
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking-requests/professional/<professional-id>
Authorization: {{token}}

### Aceitar (token do profissional)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/booking-requests/<id>/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "status": "ACCEPTED"
}

### Rejeitar com motivo (token do profissional)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/booking-requests/<id>/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "status": "REJECTED",
  "rejection_reason": "Não tenho disponibilidade nesse período."
}

### Cancelar (token do cliente)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/booking-requests/<id>/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "status": "CANCELLED"
}
